title: Music stars perform from home for Lady Gaga's livestream concert to fight coronavirus
description: Australian artists Keith Urban and Delta Goodrem join some of the world's biggest music artists performing at home for an eight-hour, livestreamed concert to support frontline healthcare workers and the World Health Organisation.
